data.description: Welcome home to this charming and newly renovated 3-bedroom, 3-full bath residence that seamlessly combines comfort and modern living. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed interior that maximizes both space and functionality. The heart of this home is the inviting kitchen, featuring updated appliances and ample storage. Sit fireside in the family room as you take in the newness of the entire main level. With 3 bedrooms, there's room for everyone, and the 3 full baths ensure convenience for the entire household. Enjoy the flexibility of a bonus living space that can be transformed into a home office, playroom, or a cozy den. Step outside to the oversized deck, perfect for entertaining or simply unwinding after a long day. The generous backyard provides a blank canvas for gardening, play, or entertainment. This home is not just about the structure; it's about creating a warm and inviting atmosphere that you'll be excited to call your own. Take advantage of this opportunity to own a beautifully renovated home that perfectly balances style and practicality. Your new chapter begins here!
